Machakos county should solve the deteriorating sanitation in Athi River and Mlolongo towns, Athi River deputy county commissioner Geoffrey Omoding&rsquo; (pictured) has said. He said the filthy situationmay lead to dieseas outbreak. &ldquo;There is public outcry on the pathetic condition of sanitation in the subcounty. Residents are finding it hard to live with solid waste and raw sewerage flowing in the open,&rdquo; he said.